WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
BRAZIL-NORTHEAST COAST.
DNC 01.
1. MAN OVERBOARD FROM VESSEL IN AREA BOUND BY
   05-34.8S 034-04.5W, 06-06.6S 034-29.8W,
   05-39.8S 034-52.3W, 05-10.4S 034-29.1W ON 15 JUN.
   VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP
   A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO ANY COASTAL RADIO STATION.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1802/19.
